	* Changed the ref_ptr<T> observer_ptr<>::lock() method to be
	  bool observer_ptr<>::lock(ref_ptr<T>&) to avoid the temporary
	  ref_ptr<>'s
	  being created and destroyed on the stack along with the
	  associated ref/unref() operations

