	  header, to add a
	  OSGDB_EXPORT macro to RegisterCompressorProxy, and modified the
	  findCompressor() method to look for custom compressors in
	  libraries
	  such like osgdb_compressor_name.so, which was described in the
	  wiki
	  page chapter 2.4."

