2006-08-03 13:35  robert

	* Changed:
	  
	  static TextureGLModeSet s_textureGLModeSet;
	  
	  To:
	  
	  static TextureGLModeSet& getTextureGLModeSet()
	  {
	  static TextureGLModeSet s_textureGLModeSet;
	  return s_textureGLModeSet;
	  }
	  
	  to prevent static initialization problems under static builds.

