	  osgWrappers/osgSim,
	  but not osgUtil, osgDB, osgFX, osgTerrain, osgGA and osgProducer
	  due to compile
	  errors. I am assuming that these compilers are fixable so I'm
	  checked all the
	  source code so that members of the community can help fix them.

